urce software what do we know about the developers who participate paul david joseph shapiro september 2008 mapping e science's path in the collaboration space ontological approach to monitoring infrastructure development paul david matthijs den besten june 2008 only connect academic business research collaborations and the formation of ecologies of innovation paul david j stanley metcalfe january 2008 stanford university economics department stanford center for international development public policy program site map economic summit
